          "$\\frac{\\sqrt{6} - \\sqrt{2}}{4}$",
          "$\\frac{\\sqrt{3} + 1}{2}$",
          "$\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}$"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$\\cos(45-30) = \\cos45\\cos30 + \\sin45\\sin30 = \\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2} \\cdot \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2} + \\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2} \\cdot \\frac{1}{2} = \\frac{\\sqrt{6} + \\sqrt{2}}{4}$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find the exact value of $\\tan(105^\\circ)$ using $\\tan(60^\\circ + 45^\\circ)$.",
        "options": [
