          "$2 + \\sqrt{3}$",
          "$2 - \\sqrt{3}$",
          "$-2 + \\sqrt{3}$"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$\\tan(60+45) = \\frac{\\sqrt{3} + 1}{1 - \\sqrt{3}} = \\frac{(\\sqrt{3}+1)(1+\\sqrt{3})}{(1-\\sqrt{3})(1+\\sqrt{3})} = \\frac{4 + 2\\sqrt{3}}{-2} = -2 - \\sqrt{3}$."
