        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$\\cos(5x)\\cos(3x) = \\frac{1}{2}[\\cos(5x+3x) + \\cos(5x-3x)] = \\frac{1}{2}[\\cos(8x) + \\cos(2x)]$."
